LISP Canonical Address Format (LCAF)
2017", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC8060.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document defines a canonical address format encoding used in Locator/ID Separation Protocol (LISP) control messages and in the encoding of lookup keys for the LISP Mapping Database System."];
